articles.title: Government officials honor Dianne Feinstein as defender of American values - KCRA Sacramento
articles.description: President Joe Biden praised the late Sen. Dianne Feinstein on Thursday as a dear friend and a woman of deep integrity who fought to protect what was important to America: freedom, civil liberties, security and the U.S. Constitution.
